": ""}, {"cid": 276370, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 53552, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : 而且只靠中医治好癌症绝症绝非虚传，我就知道不少案例。", "timestamp": 1598096365, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 276373, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 53552, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: ？？？真的搞笑，手术后发生转移也是很正常的情况好么", "timestamp": 1598096374, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 276390, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 53552, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你请就这水平，现代医学与中医，需要讨论？", "timestamp": 1598096715, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 276465, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 53552, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 谢谢", "timestamp": 1598097837, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 276467, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 53552, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 你自己做吧 反正我不吃抗生素十多年了~", "timestamp": 1598097864, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 277070, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 53552, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 老民科了", "timestamp": 1598110338, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 278070, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 53552, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "确实是这样的，贫穷的遮羞布罢辽", "timestamp": 1598156047, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 8, "pid": 53552, "reply": 16, "tag": null, "text": "#中西医论战\n\n小学的时候，带大我的婆婆得了结肠癌，手术治疗预计要十万。\n她的子女们有一派坚决不同意做手术，因为：1. 手术能不能完全治好是个问题（西医不治根，医生不敢保证）；2. 回家里找当地名医开中药（隔壁村就有得癌症吃中药好的）\n最后dz家也帮助了点。婆婆还是做了手术，十年过去，身体依然很健康。今年过年还来家里串门。\n\n中医的用处，大概就是在没钱的窘境下使“放弃治疗”显得没有那么残忍吧", "timestamp": 1598092137, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782608, "url": "", "vote": {}}}